    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Geth does not have fancy log rotation logic. That's up to an external program (e.g. docker can do that). We believe in separation of concerns. It's hard for us to cater for all log rotation logic, whereas it's trivial to add your own log capture and rotator in front.\r\n\r\nTL;DR If you want to rotate logs, add an appropriate application in front.",
